AGIPower is also compatible with OpenAI's next-gen Responses API. The base URL is the same as Chat Completions, with a more streamlined calling convention.

```python [Python]
from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    base_url="https://api.agipower.ai/v1", # [!code highlight]
    api_key="", # [!code highlight]
)

Create a request using the Responses API
response = client.responses.create(
    model="google/gemini-3.1-pro-preview", # [!code highlight]
    input="What is the meaning of life?" # [!code highlight]
)

print(response.output_text)
```

