- Set `{ "type": "text" }`: plain text output (default)
- Set `{ "type": "json_object" }`: JSON mode, guarantees the output is valid JSON
- Set `{ "type": "jsonschema", "jsonschema": {...} }`: Structured Outputs, strictly follow the JSON Schema

